  "title": "Forklift Driver #75023",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: FMCG Wholesaler</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Forklift Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: West – Tuas</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days / Mon-Fri (AM shift: 7.30am-4.45pm) or (PM shift: 4.45PM – 2AM) - Please choose either one</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to SGD 2500 + Allowances + AWS</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Offloading goods and materials from incoming vehicles and placing them in designated areas.</li><li>Moving inventory to pallets or crates for either storage or shipment.</li><li>Reporting any damages, shortages, or quality issues.</li><li>Transporting raw materials to production areas.</li><li>Conducting inspections on machinery to assess the need for repairs and ensure safety through routine maintenance.</li><li>Adhering to company policies and legal regulations.</li><li>Assisting in maintaining a safe and organized facility.</li><li>Efficiently organizing relocated and unloaded items to optimize space usage and neatly segregate products.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Min. 1 year of working experience</li><li>Must have forklift license</li><li>Able to commit OT</li><li>Familiar with handheld scanner & computerized warehouse system</li><li>Able to handle physical work and manual carton lifting (up to 15 kg)</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#75023 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
